      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Wiꞥſch fawedde wi Preestexus no Juhda Pilſ teem/ un fagahnija tohs Aug mus/ fur tee Swehtitaji kwehpinaſchi/ no Gebas li Bersebai/ un wiꞥſch nolaun tohs Augstumus eekſch Wa tim/ kas eekſch Josuus ta P iatta Wirfneeka Wahrtim bi tarn pa kreifo Rohku/ kad zo Wahrtim Pilſfahta ce-eet.\n"
